descriptionHtml:
Tired of the countless annoying travel information?
The True cheongju app uses pure API data from the Korea Tourism Organization to provide real and real information, except exaggerated and artificial information.

In this case, use the True cheongju app!

As well as restaurants and attractions, cultural facilities, recreational facilities, festivals and performances!
Provides all travel information for your region.
